  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until lightly browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute, until the spices are fragrant.",
    "Add the rest-meat and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ikura and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
